ygData.messageBody:
Hi. I stumbled upon this list and I'm so glad I found it. I wish I had known about it sooner.

I am Telania, prior 15th lvl bard lady.::pouts:: I died shortly after hitting my new mark in HighPass.. (them dumb Orcs). I was thinking of heading to Unrest with my RL hubby who is a 14th lvl WE Warrior. But after reading about Unrest I dont' think we're ready. Sounds like we need to mature just a tad bit more.. =)


ANYWAY, now that i've side tracked.. where is a good spot for my lvl to be? I've taken other suggestions like one,

"go to kerra isle! Good loot and easy". uh, They like forgot to mention Trains. Died quiet harshly I might add. eh

So, I will ask my brethen.. HELP?! hehe

Any suggestions?

Any and all would be appriecated.

thank you

Tel

Innoruuk
